Class ChatVideoMessenger

  • java.lang.Object
    • chat.web.model.ChatVideoMessenger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    chat.ejb.model.VideoMessenger

    public class ChatVideoMessenger
extends java.lang.Object
implements chat.ejb.model.VideoMessenger
    This VideoMessenger implementation holds the Part object for a video upload and provides functionality for relaying results of the processing performed by the file-handling service.
